SuperAdmin
==========

This crabgrass mod allow for god-like administration of all users
and groups in a particular site. 

Usage
=======

edit config/routes.rb (this should be done for you already)
  map.from_plugin :super_admin

Specify which crabgrass group will have super admin power in sites.yml:

<begin>
default:
  name: crabgrass
  domain: localhost
  email_sender: 'crabgrass-system@localhost'
  secret: 'd24833cab5fafcd17f2c555f7663c0524a938e5ed6df2af8'
  pagination_size: 29
  super_admin_group_id: 1
<end>

If you want the moderation capability of super_admin, 
add the migration to crabgrass:

% script/generate plugin_migration
% rake db:migrate

restart rails and browse to: http://localhost:3000/admin
